The bigger the sacrifice, the bigger the leap. Hi new world... So much comes to truth at this time about karmic attachments - what are they? They are subconscious manifestations of what we hold true.

This attachment is called 'karmic' in nature because we continuously experience it in different forms until we reveal the knowledge obtained to transcend it. This is an ENERGY that does attach itself to you because of YOUR energetic vibration.. It all starts with you.

My karmic attachment was 'the dark cupid'.. Lovers with all the traits of a God, who chose to be lesser deities through ego alignment.
Now the reason that the 'dark cupid' was my karmic attachment is because part of my karma was about playing small & also acting like a lesser deity.. An even lesser deity than the one they were portraying. A dark Cupid always knows your power, even when you don't.

And these types of karmic attachments do tend to mirror TwinFlame relationships or high vibrational soul matches.

To truly know the difference between a dark Cupid/karmic attachment & soul love you have to know yourself.
A dark Cupid will always feel a little bit dead. Ice cold inside but they will be very adapt at mimicking emotions of others.

So in a dark Cupid, you need to watch out for behaviours that mirror schizophrenia or a split in identity//personality.

Check in later for signs to help you spot a karmic attachment/dark Cupid.

Ostatnio dużo osób wrzuca filmiki z progresami dynamiki co mnie bardzo cieszy. Często wrzucane są filmiki z różnymi fajnymi trickami jak np. Muscle up 360 z tym, że... no właśnie to nie jest muscle up 360. Dużo trenujących ludzi myli elementy przez co czasem robi się zamieszanie chociażby nawet w sędziowaniu na zawodach. Podsyłam filmik między różnicą muscle up 360 a dwoma oddzielnymi elementami muscle up + 360. Technika na ten okres byle jaka ale myślę, że widać wyraźną różnicę. Zapraszam do wyrażania swojej opini, Siła !
